author: craigmcc
msg: Commit an "svn copy tiles sandbox/tiles" command that establishes a starting
point for (re)converting the integrated with Struts version of Tiles to a
standalone version.  The necessary refactoring will take place with subsequent
commits, which will maintain version history courtesy of Subversion.

author: craigmcc
msg: Commit "svn move tiles tiles-original" to save the original snapshot of
Standalone Tiles, so that a new one can be created (from scratch, and
saving version history) from the trunk version of Integrated Tiles.
